: Kickstarter","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"8374","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamefamily/8374/crowdfunding-kickstarter","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamefamily/8374/crowdfunding-kickstarter"},{"name":"Players: Games with Solitaire Rules","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"5666","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamefamily/5666/players-games-with-solitaire-rules","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamefamily/5666/players-games-with-solitaire-rules"},{"name":"Players: Two-Player Only Games","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"61979","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamefamily/61979/players-two-player-only-games","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamefamily/61979/players-two-player-only-games"},{"name":"Series: Flamecraft","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"111279","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamefamily/111279/series-flamecraft","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamefamily/111279/series-flamecraft"},{"name":"Theme: Anthropomorphic Animals","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"65774","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamefamily/65774/theme-anthropomorphic-animals","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamefamily/65774/theme-anthropomorphic-animals"}],"videogamebg":[],"boardgamesubdomain":[{"name":"Abstract Games","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"4666","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/boardgamesubdomain/4666/abstract-games","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgamesubdomain/4666/abstract-games"}],"boardgameaccessory":[],"cardset":[{"name":"Cardboard Alchemy deluxe edition (2025)","sortindex":"1","objecttype":"family","objectid":"111028","primarylink":0,"itemstate":"approved","href":"/cardset/111028/cardboard-alchemy-deluxe-edition-2025","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/cardset/111028/cardboard-alchemy-deluxe-edition-2025"}]},"linkcounts":{"boardgamedesigner":1,"boardgamesolodesigner":0,"boardgameartist":1,"boardgamepublisher":2,"boardgamedeveloper":1,"boardgamegraphicdesigner":0,"boardgamesculptor":1,"boardgameeditor":0,"boardgamewriter":0,"boardgameinsertdesigner":0,"boardgamehonor":2,"boardgamecategory":2,"boardgamemechanic":2,"boardgameexpansion":0,"boardgameversion":3,"expandsboardgame":0,"boardgameintegration":0,"contains":0,"containedin":0,"reimplementation":0,"reimplements":0,"boardgamefamily":7,"videogamebg":0,"boardgamesubdomain":1,"boardgameaccessory":0,"cardset":1},"secondarynamescount":0,"alternatenamescount":1,"primaryname":{"nameid":"2571674","name":"Flamecraft Duals","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Flamecraft Duals"},"alternatenames":[{"nameid":"2684911","name":"Мастера пламени: Дуэль"}],"description":"<p>Ever wondered what the dragons of <em>Flamecraft</em> do on their lunch break? Play <em><strong>Flamecraft Duals</strong></em>, of course! Set in the world of <em>Flamecraft</em>, <em>Duals</em> is a two-player travel-friendly game of pattern-making and quick, puzzly fun! You will meet the artisan dragons again with new powers, and this time the challenge is to get your dragons in a row. As you draw dragons, you might get lucky and come across a rare dual-colored Hydragon, with double the artisanal skills! As you play, the board will fill up with adorable dragons, stacking and soaring across the table, and you will work to fire-up their abilities, make matches, and complete shop cards.</p>\n\n<p><em>Flamecraft Duals</em> is a two-player abstract pattern-building game that takes about 30 minutes to play. Each round, a player draws a dragon from the bag and places it on the shared central board. Every dragon type has a special ability that can be fired up to draw more dragons or rearrange those already on the board. You want to match three dragons on the board to the pattern on the shop cards in your hand to score them. Once all the dragons are drawn from the bag, the game ends and the player with the highest score wins.</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<p>COMPONENTS:<br />\nCardboard:<br />\n1 Game board (29.5x18.5cm, integrated into magnetic latched game box)</p>\n\n<p>Wood:<br />\n2 Player card holders (17x2.5x1.2cm; engraved in Deluxe Edition)</p>\n\n<p>Metal:<br />\n6 Dragon Coins (Deluxe Edition; chrome, 27mm hex x 3mm)</p>\n\n<p>Plastic:<br />\n1 Fountain Dragon miniature (Deluxe Edition; green 26mm hex base x 46mm tall)</p>\n\n<p>43 Acrylic chips with heat transfer designs (27mm dia. x 6mm):<br />\n&bull; 36 Artisan Dragon chips (6x each yellow Bread, light blue Crystal, dark blue Iron, red Meat, green Plant, purple Potion)<br />\n&bull; 6 Dual Dragon chips (1x each Crystal/Bread, Bread/Meat, Meat/Plant, Crystal/Iron, Iron/Potion, Potion/Plant)<br />\n&bull; 1 Buddy chip (pink Fancy Dragon)</p>\n\n<p>59 cards (63x88mm plastic):<br />\n&bull; 42 Shop cards (beige Shop back; 30 worth 2VP, 12 worth 3VP)<br />\n&bull; 6 Fountain cards (green fountain dragon backs, all worth 3VP)<br />\n&bull; 8 Fancy Dragon cards (pink swirl backs; 4 Active, 4 Passive effects)<br />\n&bull; 2 Reference cards for 2-players (double-sided Turn Sequence &amp; End of Game / Fire Up Chart)<br />\n&bull; 1 Solo Reference card (double-sided Solo conditions / Reputation scale)</p>\n\n<p>Rule booklet (16 p.).</p>\n\n","website":{"url":"https://cardboardalchemy.com/flamecraft-duals/","title":"Flamecraft Duals - Cardboard Alchemy"},"imageid":"8706498","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/wIpk8_5xO9Hh3cAPvWAslQ__small/img/rLl3hBXX7FLdQQyCfEXyt_HIN8M=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic8706498.png","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/wIpk8_5xO9Hh3cAPvWAslQ__micro/img/LycAvhIhNIqN9CkFvTWz48p_r9Q=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic8706498.png","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/wIpk8_5xO9Hh3cAPvWAslQ__square/img/QavHYosbk